/*
TODO:

- Re-Consider replacing single quote with plus in default layer.

- Replace Alt+num to move between desktops. Use Win+num instead.
    - This is to avoid false positives of "alt" in applications while switching on both Win and Linux.
    - keyd: replace keybinds for Capslock layer.

- Numbers with alt (left hand).
    - Or maybe just use software for this.
        - Same with Control.
        - Not the idea, though.

- Modal movement layer.
    - Add deletion sub-layer
    - Add selection sub-layer
